data.description: Charming home with many extras in excellent Webb City location! Full brick, covered front porch, beautiful entry, open floor plan, granite counters, newer wood vinyl plank flooring, nice pantry plus bonus storage nook in laundry room, split bedroom design, great primary bedroom and bath features tile walk in shower, double sinks, walk in closet, covered patio and extended open patio overlooks fenced back yard, well maintained, french drain, wonderful landscaping and curb appeal!
